<slide title="The Portable Document Format">
<blurb title="Benefits of PDF Documents"/>
    <list>
    <bullet>Accessable on any modern platform</bullet>
    <bullet>Allows for WYSIWYG formatting and printing</bullet>
    <bullet>Password protectable, difficult to modify</bullet>
    </list>
<blurb title="Drawbacks of PDF"/>
    <list>
        <bullet>Requires a third party viewer (free)</bullet>
        <bullet>Considerably more difficult to work with from within PHP</bullet>
    </list>
</slide>